 /*
            check user keycode via event lambda NOT AllowedKey enum.
            if its a valid word -> update UI:
                change current LetterBox label then move on to the next one
            if user clicks enter:
                check if we are at the end of column. If so,
                                                        then check answer then move on to the next row
            if user clicks backspace:
                set current letterbox label to an empty string & go back to the previous letterbox
             */